com.lightstreamer.interfaces.metadata

Class MpnSubscriptionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lightstreamer.interfaces.metadata.MpnSubscriptionInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MpnSubscriptionInfo.MpnApnsSubscriptionInfo

    public abstract class MpnSubscriptionInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class used by Lightstreamer to provide value objects to the calls to methods MetadataProvider.notifyMpnSubscriptionActivation(String, TableInfo, MpnSubscriptionInfo) and MetadataProvider.notifyMpnSubscriptionDeactivation(String, TableInfo, MpnSubscriptionInfo). The attributes of every Push Notification to be activated or deactivated has to be written to a MpnSubscriptionInfo instance. See subclasses for platform specific details.
    Edition Note:
    Push Notifications are not supported in Moderato edition.
